<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Standards are established in accordance with the provisions of the second paragraph of Article 15 of the Act Governing Food Sanitation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The safety tolerances of atomic dust and radioactivity contamination in foods:

┌───────────┬─────────┬────────┐
│        ＼    Food    │Milk products and │Other foods     │
│category  ＼          │infant foods      │                │
│Radioactive ＼        │                  │                │
│nucleus       ＼      │                  │                │
├───────────┼─────────┼────────┤
│131                   │Not more than     │Not more than   │
│   I                  │55Bq/kg           │300 Bq/kg       │
├───────────┼─────────┼────────┤
│134   137             │Not more than 370 │Not more than   │
│   Cs+   Cs           │Bq/kg             │370 Bq/kg 　　  │
└───────────┴─────────┴────────┘

]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Standards shall be implemented from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
